text: musa ila prarthincadu: "O ma prabhu! Niscayanga, nivu phir'aun ku mariyu atani nayakulaku ihaloka jivitanlo vaibhavam mariyu sampadalanu prasadincavu. O ma prabhu! Varini (prajalanu) ni margam nundi tappincatanika ivi? O ma prabhu! Vari sampadalanu dhvansam ceyi, vari hrdayalapai kathinavasthanu kalugajeyi, endukante varu kathina siksanu cusentavaraku visvasincaru
